  "texts": [
    "By fine-tuning a math-specialized LLM (Mathstral-7B-v0.1) using LoRA and leveraging ensemble disagreement during inference, our system achieved top-tier results across all tracks-ranking 1 st in Providing Guidance and within the top 5 in all others.",
    "Our findings highlight the effectiveness of combining domain-specific instruction tuning with disagreement-aware prediction filtering for educational feedback assessment.",
    "Future work will explore cross-domain generalization and dynamic calibration strategies to further enhance robustness."
